2}, {\"ngram\": \"the record book\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The race will begin at the Hotel de Ville and end at the Esplanade de Invalides, the final resting place of Napoleon.\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1358, \"end\": 1366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Napoleon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.805092410211435e-37, \"text\": \"Napoleon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Napoleon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Napoleon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The race\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1258}, {\"ngram\": \"the Hotel de Ville\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"the Esplanade de Invalides\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"the final resting place\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike other marathons, it's not a series of repeated loops - it's one big one.\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1447, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other marathons\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1390}, {\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1409}, {\"ngram\": \"repeated loops\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The route will follow that of more than 7,000 Parisians who marched in protest (the Women's March on Versailles in October 1789), leading to the ratification of the Universal Declaration of the Rights of Man and of the Citizen.\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1676, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The route\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 7,000 Parisians\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"protest\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"the Women's March\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1546}, {\"ngram\": \"Versailles\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1560}, {\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1571}, {\"ngram\": \"the ratification\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"the Universal 